# UFR-022 lib-docs — local snapshot cache, untracked, regenerated on demand.
# Only INDEX.json + README.md + .gitignore + */LESSONS.md are tracked
# (also enforced by the root .gitignore). This file is the second line of
# defense and the per-folder documentation of intent.

# Per-lib generated artifacts (untracked)
*/VERSION
*/snapshot-*.md
*/sources.json
*/PATTERNS.md

# Anything else under a lib folder that isn't LESSONS.md
# (root .gitignore handles the whitelist; this is belt-and-suspenders)
